<!--the one ref is a note, not a source--> '''Air Optix''' is a brand of breathable [[contact lens]]es made by [[Ciba Vision]]. They are soft contact lenses made from a [[silicone]] [[Gel#Hydrogels|hydrogel]] material consisting of approximately 67% lotrafilcon B (except in Japan),<ref name=japan/> 33% water, and have a patented surface treatment to resist deposits for more comfortable lens wear. O2 Optix lenses are for daily wear and extended wear for up to six continuous nights.
